<p dir="auto"><a href="https://github.com/csstools/postcss-plugins/tree/main/plugins/postcss-focus-visible">PostCSS Focus Visible</a> duplicates rules using the <code>:focus-visible</code> pseudo-class
with a <code>.focus-visible</code> class selector, the same selector used by the
<a href="https://github.com/WICG/focus-visible">focus-visible polyfill</a>.</p>
